#: data/nautilus-autorun-software.desktop.in:2
msgid "Run Software"
msgstr "Egzekite Lojisyèl"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:5 data/org.gnome.Nautilus.desktop.in.in:2
#: src/nautilus-mime-actions.c:102 src/nautilus-portal.c:535
#: src/resources/ui/nautilus-window.ui:123
msgid "Files"
msgstr "Fichye"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:6 data/org.gnome.Nautilus.desktop.in.in:3
msgid "Access and organize files"
msgstr "Aksede ak òganize fichye yo"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:8
msgid ""
"Files, also known as Nautilus, is the default file manager of the GNOME desktop. It "
"provides a simple and integrated way of managing your files and browsing your file "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Fichye, ke yo rele tou Nautilus, se jesyonè fichye pa defo biwo GNOME. Li ofri yon "
"fason senp ak entegre pou jere fichye ou yo ak navige nan sistèm fichye ou."

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:12
msgid ""
"Nautilus supports all the basic functions of a file manager and more. It can search and "
"manage your files and folders, both locally and on a network, read and write data to "
"and from removable media, run scripts, and launch apps. It has three views: Icon Grid, "
"Icon List, and Tree List. Its functions can be extended with plugins and scripts."
msgstr ""
"Nautilus sipòte tout fonksyon debaz yon jesyonè fichye e plis toujou. Li ka fè rechèch "
"ak jere fichye ak dosye ou yo, ni lokalman ni sou yon rezo, li ak ekri done sou aparèy "
"detachable, egzekite scripts, epi lanse aplikasyon. Li gen twa vi: Griy Ikon, Lis Ikon, "
"ak Lis Pye Bwa. Fonksyon li yo ka elaji avèk modil ekstensyon ak scripts."

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:60 src/nautilus-files-view.c:9661
msgid "Grid View"
msgstr "Wè an Griy"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:64 src/nautilus-files-view.c:9668
msgid "List View"
msgstr "Wè an Lis"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:68 src/nautilus-search-directory-file.c:230
#: src/nautilus-search-directory-file.c:269
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Rechèch"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.metainfo.xml.in.in:72
msgid "Selection of Multiple Files"
msgstr "Seleksyon Plizyè Fichye"

#. Translators: Search terms to find this application. Do NOT translate or localize the semicolons! The list MUST also end with a semicolon!
#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.desktop.in.in:5
msgid "folder;manager;explore;disk;filesystem;nautilus;"
msgstr "dosye;jesyonè;eksplore;disk;sistèmfichye;nautilus;"

#: data/org.gnome.Nautilus.desktop.in.in:20
msgid "New Window"
msgstr "Nouvo Fenèt"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:82
msgid "Always use the location entry, instead of the pathbar"
msgstr "Toujou itilize antre lokalizasyon an, olye de ba pou chemen an"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:83
msgid ""
"If set to true, Files will always use a textual input entry for the location toolbar, "
"instead of the pathbar."
msgstr ""
"Si mete sou vre, Fichye ap toujou itilize yon antre tèks pou ba zouti lokalizasyon an, "
"olye de ba pou chemen an."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:87
msgid "Where to perform recursive search"
msgstr "Ki kote pou fè rechèch nan sous-dosye yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:88
msgid ""
"Locations in which Files should search subfolders. Available values are “local-only”, "
"“always”, “never”."
msgstr ""
"Lokalizasyon kote Fichye ta dwe fè rechèch nan sous-dosye yo. Valè disponib yo se « "
"local-only », « always », « never »."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:92
msgid "Filter the search dates using either last used or last modified"
msgstr "Filtre dat rechèch yo lè l sèvi avèk dènye itilize oswa dènye modifye"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:93
msgid "Filter the search dates using either last used or last modified."
msgstr "Filtre dat rechèch yo lè l sèvi avèk dènye itilize oswa dènye modifye."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:97
msgid "Whether to show a context menu item to delete permanently"
msgstr "Si pou montre yon atik meni kontèks pou efase definitivman"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:98
msgid ""
"If set to true, Files will show a delete permanently context menu item to bypass the "
"Trash."
msgstr ""
"Si mete sou vre, Fichye ap montre yon atik meni kontèks efase definitivman pou kontoune "
"Poubèl la."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:102
msgid "Whether to show context menu items to create links from copied or selected files"
msgstr ""
"Si pou montre atik meni kontèks pou kreye lyen apati fichye kopye oswa seleksyone yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:103
msgid ""
"If set to true, Files will show context menu items to create links from the copied or "
"selected files."
msgstr ""
"Si mete sou vre, Fichye ap montre atik meni kontèks pou kreye lyen apati fichye kopye "
"oswa seleksyone yo."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:108
msgid "When to show number of items in a folder"
msgstr "Kilè pou montre kantite eleman nan yon dosye"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:109
msgid ""
"Speed tradeoff for when to show the number of items in a folder. If set to “always” "
"then always show item counts, even if the folder is on a remote server. If set to "
"“local-only” then only show counts for local file systems. If set to “never” then never "
"bother to compute item counts."
msgstr ""
"Konpwomi vitès pou kilè pou montre kantite eleman nan yon dosye. Si mete sou « always » "
"ap toujou montre konte atik yo, menm si dosye a sou yon sèvè a distans. Si mete sou « "
"local-only » ap montre konte yo sèlman pou sistèm fichye lokal yo. Si mete sou « never "
"» pa janm pran pwoblèm pou kalkile konte atik yo."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:113
msgid "Type of click used to launch/open files"
msgstr "Tip klik yo itilize pou lanse/ouvri fichye yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:114
msgid ""
"Possible values are “single” to launch files on a single click, or “double” to launch "
"them on a double click."
msgstr ""
"Valè posib yo se « yon sèl klik » pou lanse fichye yo sou yon klik senp, oswa « de klik "
"» pou lanse yo sou yon klik doub."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:118
msgid "Show the package installer for unknown MIME types"
msgstr "Montre enstale pake a pou tip MIME enkoni"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:119
msgid ""
"Whether to show the user a package installer dialog in case an unknown MIME type is "
"opened, in order to search for an app to handle it."
msgstr ""
"Si pou montre itilizatè a yon dyalòg enstale pake nan ka yo ouvri yon tip MIME enkoni, "
"pou fè rechèch pou yon aplikasyon pou jere li."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:123
msgid "Use extra mouse button events in Files"
msgstr "Itilize evènman bouton souri siplemantè nan Fichye"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:124
msgid ""
"For users with mice that have “Forward” and “Back” buttons, this key will determine if "
"any action is taken inside of Files when either is pressed."
msgstr ""
"Pou itilizatè ki gen souri ak bouton « Avanse » ak « Fè bak », opsyon sa a ap detèmine "
"si gen yon aksyon ki fèt andedan Fichye lè yo peze youn nan yo."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:128
msgid "Mouse button to activate the “Forward” command in browser window"
msgstr "Bouton souri pou aktive kòmand « Avanse » nan fenèt navigatè a"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:129
msgid ""
"For users with mice that have buttons for “Forward” and “Back”, this key will set which "
"button activates the “Forward” command in a browser window. Possible values range "
"between 6 and 14."
msgstr ""
"Pou itilizatè ki gen souri ak bouton pou « Avanse » ak « Fè bak », opsyon sa a ap "
"defini ki bouton ki aktive kòmand « Avanse » nan yon fenèt navigatè. Valè posib yo ant "
"6 ak 14."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:133
msgid "Mouse button to activate the “Back” command in browser window"
msgstr "Bouton souri pou aktive kòmand « Fè bak » nan fenèt navigatè a"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:134
msgid ""
"For users with mice that have buttons for “Forward” and “Back”, this key will set which "
"button activates the “Back” command in a browser window. Possible values range between "
"6 and 14."
msgstr ""
"Pou itilizatè ki gen souri ak bouton pou « Avanse » ak « Fè bak », opsyon sa a ap "
"defini ki bouton ki aktive kòmand « Fè bak » nan yon fenèt navigatè. Valè posib yo ant "
"6 ak 14."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:139
msgid "When to show thumbnails of files"
msgstr "Kilè pou montre ti imaj fichye yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:140
msgid ""
"Speed trade-off for when to show a file as a thumbnail. If set to “always” then always "
"thumbnail, even if the folder is on a remote server. If set to “local-only” then only "
"show thumbnails for local file systems. If set to “never” then never bother to "
"thumbnail files, just use a generic icon. Despite what the name may suggest, this "
"applies to any previewable file type."
msgstr ""
"Konpwomi vitès pou kilè pou montre yon fichye kòm yon ti imaj. Si mete sou « Toujou » "
"ap toujou fè ti imaj, menm si dosye a sou yon sèvè a distans. Si mete sou « lokal "
"sèlman » ap montre ti imaj sèlman pou sistèm fichye lokal yo. Si mete sou « jamè » pa "
"janm pran pwoblèm pou fè ti imaj fichye yo, jis itilize yon ikon jenerik. Malgre sa non "
"an ka sijere, sa aplike a nenpòt tip fichye ki ka gen aperçu."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:144
msgid "Maximum image size for thumbnailing"
msgstr "Gwosè imaj maksimòm pou fè ti imaj"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:145
msgid ""
"Images over this size (in megabytes) won’t be thumbnailed. The purpose of this setting "
"is to avoid thumbnailing large images that may take a long time to load or use lots of "
"memory."
msgstr ""
"Imaj ki depase gwosè sa a (an megaokte) pap fè ti imaj yo. Objektif anviwònman sa a se "
"pou evite fè ti imaj pou gwo imaj ki ka pran anpil tan pou chaje oswa itilize anpil "
"memwa."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:152
msgid "Default sort order"
msgstr "Lòd klasman pa defo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:153
msgid ""
"The default sort-order for items in the icon view. Possible values are “name”, “size”, "
"“type”, “mtime”, “atime” and “starred”."
msgstr ""
"Lòd klasman pa defo pou eleman yo nan vi ikòn yo. Valè posib yo se « non »,« gwosè », « "
"tip », « dat modifikasyon », « dat dènye modifikasyon » ak « favori »."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:157
msgid "Reverse sort order in new windows"
msgstr "Envèse lòd klasman nan nouvo fenèt yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:158
msgid ""
"If true, files in new windows will be sorted in reverse order. I.e., if sorted by name, "
"then instead of sorting the files from “a” to “z”, they will be sorted from “z” to “a”; "
"if sorted by size, instead of being incrementally they will be sorted decrementally."
msgstr ""
"Si vre, fichye nan nouvo fenèt yo ap klase nan lòd envès. Sa vle di, si yo klase pa "
"non, olye yo klase fichye yo apati « a » pou rive « z », y ap klase yo apati « z » pou "
"rive « a »; si yo klase pa gwosè, olye yo ogmante y ap klase yo diminye."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:168
msgid "Default folder viewer"
msgstr "Vizyèl dosye pa defo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:169
msgid ""
"When a folder is visited this viewer is used. Possible values are “list-view”, and "
"“icon-view”."
msgstr ""
"Lè yo vizite yon dosye yo, itilize vizyèl sa a. Valè posib yo se « wè an lis » ak « wè "
"nan ikòn »."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:173
msgid "Whether to show hidden files"
msgstr "Si pou montre fichye kache yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:174
msgid ""
"This key is deprecated and ignored. The “show-hidden” key from “org.gtk.Settings."
"FileChooser” is now used instead."
msgstr ""
"Opsyon sa a depase epi li inyore. Yo itilize opsyon « afiche eleman kache » ki soti nan "
"« org.gtk.Settings.FileChooser » kounye a olye."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:178
msgid "Whether GTK 4 settings migration happened"
msgstr "Si migrasyon paramèt GTK 4 te fèt"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:179
msgid ""
"Whether settings shared with GtkFileChooser have been migrated from their GTK 3 keys to "
"the GTK 4 ones."
msgstr ""
"Si paramèt ki pataje ak GtkFileChooser yo te migre soti nan kle GTK 3 yo pou ale nan "
"kle GTK 4 yo."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:183
msgid "Whether to open the hovered folder after a timeout when drag and drop operation"
msgstr ""
"Si pou ouvri dosye ki siwole a apre yon tan limite pandan yon operasyon glise ak depoze"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:184
msgid ""
"If this is set to true, when performing a drag and drop operation the hovered folder "
"will open automatically after a timeout."
msgstr ""
"Si sa a mete sou vre, lè w ap fè yon operasyon glise ak depoze, dosye ki siwole a ap "
"ouvri otomatikman apre yon tan limite."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:188
msgid "Whether to have full text search enabled by default when opening a new window/tab"
msgstr "Si pou gen rechèch tèks konplè aktive pa defo lè w ap ouvri yon nouvo fenèt/onglè"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:189
msgid ""
"If set to true, Files will also match the file contents besides the name. This toggles "
"the default active state, which can still be overridden in the search popover"
msgstr ""
"Si mete sou vre, Fichye ap koresponn tou ak kontni fichye a ansanm ak non an. Sa a "
"chanje eta aktif pa defo a, ki ka toujou anile nan fenèt kontèks rechèch la"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:193
msgid "How to display file timestamps in the views"
msgstr "Ki jan pou montre timestamps fichye yo nan vi yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:194
msgid ""
"If set to 'simple', Files will show Today and Yesterday with time, otherwise the exact "
"date without time. If set to 'detailed', it will always show the exact date and time."
msgstr ""
"Si mete sou 'senp', Fichye ap montre Jodi a ak Yè ak lè, otreman dat egzak la san lè. "
"Si mete sou 'detaye', li ap toujou montre dat ak lè egzak la."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:201
msgid "Default format for compressing files"
msgstr "Fòma pa defo pou konprese fichye yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:202
msgid "The format that will be selected when compressing files."
msgstr "Fòma ki ap seleksyone lè w ap konprese fichye yo."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:209
msgid "List of possible captions on icons"
msgstr "Lis lejann posib sou ikon yo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:210
msgid ""
"A list of captions below an icon in the icon view. The actual number of captions shown "
"depends on the zoom level. Some possible values are: “size”, “type”, “date_modified”, "
"“owner”, “group”, “permissions”, and “mime_type”."
msgstr ""
"Yon lis lejann anba yon ikon nan vi ikon yo. Kantite aktyèl lejann yo montre depann de "
"nivo zoum nan. Kèk valè posib yo se: « gwosè », « tip », « dat modifikasyon », « mèt », "
"« gwoup », « pèmisyon », ak « tip mime »."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:219
msgid "Default icon view zoom level"
msgstr "Nivo zoum vi ikon pa defo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:230
msgid "Default list view zoom level"
msgstr "Nivo zoum vi lis pa defo"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:234
msgid "Columns visible in list view"
msgstr "Kolòn vizib nan vi lis la"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:238
msgid "Column order in list view"
msgstr "Lòd kolòn nan vi lis la"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:242
msgid "Use tree view"
msgstr "Itilize vi pye bwa"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:243
msgid "Whether a tree should be used for list view navigation instead of a flat list."
msgstr "Si yo ta dwe itilize yon pye bwa pou navigasyon vi lis olye de yon lis plat."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:250 data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:260
msgid "Initial size of the window"
msgstr "Gwosè inisyal fenèt la"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:251 data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:261
msgid "A tuple containing the initial width and height of the app window."
msgstr "Yon gwoup ki genyen lajè ak wotè inisyal fenèt aplikasyon an."

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:255
msgid "Whether the navigation window should be maximized"
msgstr "Si fenèt navigasyon an ta dwe maksimize"

#: data/org.gnome.nautilus.gschema.xml:256
msgid "Whether the navigation window should be maximized by default."
msgstr "Si fenèt navigasyon an ta dwe maksimize pa defo."

#: eel/eel-stock-dialogs.c:194
msgid "You can stop this operation by clicking cancel."
msgstr "Ou ka sispann operasyon sa a lè w klike sou anile."

